        <div class="cover-image flat d-flex justify-content-center flex-column"><div data-is-viewable="" class="cover-image__image"><a href="/toc/radiographics/27/4" title="Go to RadioGraphics " class="d-block"><img src="/cms/10.1148/radiographics.2007.27.issue-4/asset/14a16856-3014-1685-0301-a1685603014a/radiographics.2007.27.issue-4.cover.gif" alt="Go to RadioGraphics " loading="lazy"/></a></div></div>
<div class="core-journal-description"><div property="isPartOf" typeof="Periodical"><span property="name">RadioGraphics</span></div><div class="core-enumeration"><span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationVolume">Volume <span property="volumeNumber">27</span></span> • <span property="isPartOf" typeof="PublicationIssue">Number <span property="issueNumber">4</span></span> • <span property="datePublished">Jul 1 2007</span></div><div class="core-pagination"><span class="heading">Pages</span>: <span class="content"><span property="pageStart">989</span> - <span property="pageEnd">1004</span></span></div><div class="core-pmid"><span class="heading">PubMed</span>: <a class="content" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17620463/" property="sameAs" target="_blank" title="Link to PubMed">17620463</a></div></div></div></section><section class="core-copyright"><h4>Copyright</h4><div role="paragraph">© RSNA, 2007.</div></section><section class="core-history"><h4>History</h4><div><b class="core-label">Published online</b>: Jul 1 2007</div></section><section class="core-permissions"><h4>Permissions</h4><div>Request permissions for this article.</div><div><a class="btn" href="https://marketplace.copyright.com/rs-ui-web/mp/search/all/10.1148%2Frg.274065171">Request Permissions</a></div></section><section class="core-article-notes"><h4>Notes</h4><div role="paragraph">The origins, manifestations, and treatment of the multisystemic connective-tissue disorder known as Marfan syndrome are reviewed, and the most important radiologic features in the cardiovascular, musculoskeletal, pulmonary, and other systems are described in detail.</div></section></section><section id="tab-contributors" role="tabpanel"><h3>Authors</h3><section class="core-authors"><h4>Affiliations</h4><div id="con1" property="author" typeof="Person"><div class="heading"><span property="givenName">Hong Il</span> <span property="familyName">Ha</span>, <span property="honorificSuffix">MD</span></div><div class="content">